casebody.data:
Certiorari Granted.

(See also No. 102, Misc., supra.) No. 789. Federal Power Commission v. East Ohio Gas Co. et al. United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit. Solicitor General Perlman and Bradford Ross for petitioner. Herbert S. Duffy, Attorney-General of Ohio, Kenneth B. Johnston, Assistant Attorney General, William B. Cockley, Walter J. Milde, Wm. A. Dougherty and Sturgis Warner for respondents.

Certiorari granted.

Mr. Justice Burton took no part in the consideration or decision of this application.
